<p begin='00:00:09.576' end='00:00:14.815' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; FROM COMEDY CENTRAL&apos;S WORLD<br/>NEWS HEADQUARTERS IN NEW YORK,</span></p>
