<p begin='00:01:31.925' end='00:01:33.026' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; Jon: RACISM IS OVER!</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:33.060' end='00:01:37.931' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>[CHEERS AND APPLAUSE]<br/>OF COURSE, THE JUSTICES WERE<br/>JUST</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:37.965' end='00:01:42.002' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>CODIFYING WHAT MANY OF US HAD<br/>KNOWN FOR A VERY LONG TIME.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:42.035' end='00:01:44.037' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; AMERICA TREATS PEOPLE<br/>EQUALLY.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:44.071' end='00:01:46.373' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>WE HAVE A BLACK PRESIDENT.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:46.406' end='00:01:49.843' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>EUROPE EVEN HAS NEVER HAD A<br/>BLACK PRESIDENT.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:49.877' end='00:01:52.746' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>&gt;&gt; UNFORTUNATELY FOR LIBERALS<br/>THERE&apos;S NO RACISM IN AMERICA.</span></p>
<p begin='00:01:52.779' end='00:01:55.382' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>THERE&apos;S MORE CHOLERA IN AMERICA<br/>THAN THERE IS RACISM.</span></p>
