<p begin='00:03:34.381' end='00:03:39.553' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>IT&apos;S THAT AGE OLD STORY, &quot;YEAH,<br/>I&apos;M RACIST BUT MY (bleep) AND MY</span></p>
