<p begin='00:04:14.321' end='00:04:19.126' tts:textAlign='left'  space='preserve'><span style='block'>IF YOU THINK AN OLD MAN TELLING<br/>HIS GIRLFRIEND IT&apos;S COOL IF SHE</span></p>
